Grazioso Salvare Rescue Animal Dashboard
Project Functionality
This dashboard allows Grazioso Salvare staff to browse the Austin Animal Center Outcomes dataset and filter it by search-and-rescue category. The dashboard includes:
•	A header with the Grazioso Salvare logo and developer identifier
•	Radio button filters for Water Rescue, Mountain or Wilderness Rescue, Disaster or Individual Tracking, and Reset
•	An interactive, sortable, paginated data table that updates based on the selected filter
•	A pie chart showing breed distribution of the filtered results
•	A geolocation map showing the location of the selected animal
